    <p>
      Faith's main requirements were to work within Squarespace, keep the original media, and create
      a modern feel. She also encouraged me to use AI, which I applied to refine the written
      content. Working solely in Squarespace, I iterated on the site through three rounds,
      explaining my decisions each time and incorporating feedback until all requirements were met.
    </p>
