{# DESIGN DECISIONS #}
<section class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-[1fr_3fr] gap-5 pb-8">
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-end gap-2">
    <h1 class="text-xl font-medium tracking-wide pt-0.5">DECISIONS</h1>
    <p>
      I structured the user flow around three priorities: present the brand, prioritize shopping,
      then provide resources for deeper engagement. An interactive hero section leads the page,
      followed by the best-selling products to encourage conversions. Site-wide content was
      rewritten with AI assistance to make it concise, clear, and aligned with the original meaning.
      Brand identity was maintained through earthy tones, re-used written material and imagery, and
      the existing Squarespace template. The site layout uses clearly labeled sections with color
      changes and borders for easy scanning, while shop and blog pages were reorganized into
      scannable grids. The mobile layout was fully reworked to accommodate these changes.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
